<item>
            <title>[ISS-151] Simple Deployment Options</title>
                <link>http://jira.perfect.org:8080/browse/ISS-151</link>
                <project id="10007" key="ISS">Issues</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;One of our goals is to make Perfect both easy to setup for development, but also make it easy to deploy on cloud services. Our current hit-list for build packs/tiles/whatever-you-call-it and detailed instructions for deployment looks like this (in order of preference based on developer feedback);&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1) Heroku&lt;br/&gt;
2) Cloud Foundry&lt;br/&gt;
3) Docker&lt;br/&gt;
4) AWS&lt;br/&gt;
5) Azure&lt;br/&gt;
6) Google Cloud&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Anyone interested in helping out? Any additional suggestions for final deployment options?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
