&lt;p&gt;2&#12289;No git support&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Somebody HELP !!!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="10530" author="jonog" created="Tue, 21 Jun 2016 17:34:40 -0400"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi &lt;a href=&quot;http://jira.perfect.org:8080/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=linxyfe&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;linxyfe&quot;&gt;Will Zhang&lt;/a&gt; I have split your issue off to it&apos;s own thread and assigned it to be dealt with.&lt;br/&gt;
